headline: DAT 2026 Freight Focus: Gradual recovery expected for transportation providers as AI reshapes industry operations
summary: BEAVERTON, Ore., December 10, 2025--Truckload transportation providers should not expect a dramatic rebound in the freight market in 2026, according to the latest annual Freight Focus: Transportation & Logistics Outlook report from DAT Freight & Analytics.
